title: Doom 2016 Multi9 CPY NoSteam SinglePlayer
description:
Based on CPY's Release.

Languages (Depends on Setup Language): English, Deutsch, French, Russian, Polish, Portuguese, Italian, Spanish, Japanese

Full Installed Game Now uses only 44 GB of HDD Space! 
Cut: Multiplayer Maps, Snapmap

Install: Burn or Mount ISO, Run Setup.exe

Redists: DirectX, VC 2012 x86/x64, AMD Radeon Crimson 16.9.1 Win8.1 x64

Enjoy, Good Luck, Have Fun!

Release made by YURBAN

If u Have BSOD while Game Run like: "... OpenGL 4.3 ...." 
-just install latest vga drivers ;)
